                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#154v" facs="157"/><desc>A <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1035HolyMan">Holy Man Portrait</ref> and a <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1105HolyWoman">Holy Woman</ref>, Däqsǝyos and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6819Mary">St Mary</persName>(?). The woman stands behind a chair and holds something in her right hand; the man holds pen and parchment</desc></decoNote>
